Package com.cafean.client.analysis

Class RealBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cafean.Number.BaseNumber
      • com.cafean.Number.Real
        • com.cafean.client.analysis.RealBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.datatransfer.Transferable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable
    public class RealBean
extends Real
    This is a Bean implementation of Real. This includes empty functions that are required by anything that implements PibBlock. This allows for new Real extensions to be created as SubBlocks inside of a Plugin.
